          <p class="card__text">Every element in the final architecture traces back through a chain: Component → Capability → Domain → MMP Decision. Auditors can verify: "Why does this ViolationLifecycleManager component exist?" → "Because CDM Domain 4 was ACCEPTED in PV-DOM-4."</p>
          <div class="card__tags"><span class="tag">FULL TRACE CHAIN</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon--diamond"><span></span></div>
          <h4 class="card__title">Coverage validation</h4>
          <p class="card__text">The Historian caught 2 unbacked capabilities that would have become gaps in implementation. The repair cycle added the missing components before architecture was presented for approval — not after execution had already begun.</p>
          <div class="card__tags"><span class="tag">2 GAPS CAUGHT</span><span class="tag">PRE-EXECUTION</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid--3" style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
