          <p class="card__text">Pre-Mortem cards identified the multi-tenant RLS migration risk and DBOS state machine versioning risk during INTAKE — before any architecture work began. Both risks were accepted with awareness, not discovered during execution.</p>
          <div class="card__tags"><span class="tag">2 RISKS PRE-IDENTIFIED</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon--diamond"><span></span></div>
          <h4 class="card__title">Source attribution</h4>
          <p class="card__text">Every integration point was tagged: document-specified (11), domain-standard (5), or AI-proposed (5). This let the user prioritize the technology stack already chosen in the product description over speculative AI suggestions.</p>
