          <h4 class="card__title">Decision propagation</h4>
          <p class="card__text">Rejecting "AI/ML Services" as a standalone domain in Round 1 correctly excluded it from Rounds 2-4. No entities were proposed for it. No workflows reference it. No integration points target it. The rejection was atomic.</p>
          <div class="card__tags"><span class="tag">ATOMIC REJECTION</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
